name: Small kitty babble ball® interactive cat toy
description:
Perfect for your feline friends, or even the smaller dog. Makes 6 different sounds to intrigue your cat including meows, squeaks, chirps and ‘here, Kitty, Kitty!’. These fantastic Babble Balls are interactive toys that play animal sounds when touched. When play is finished, the Babble Ball turns off automatically and waits to be touched again. Your cat will think it’s actually alive! 

Durable Rigid high impact ABS construction with grooves, this Babble Ball is perfect entertainment for you and your pet!

name: Large animal sounds babble ball® dog toy
description:
The new generation has arrived! This large Babble Ball has more than 20 different realistic animal sounds including a lion, a frog, a coyote howl, cats, pigs and lots of birds and barking dogs. These fantastic Babble Balls are interactive toys that play animal sounds when touched. The improved technology is so sensitive it can be triggered by your dog breathing on it, or just by the vibration when walking past it. When play is finished, the Babble Ball turns off automatically and waits to be touched again. Your dog will think it’s actually alive! 

Durable high impact ABS construction, triple the sounds, improved sound quality and now with replaceable batteries - great fun for you and your pooch! 7cms in diameter.

description:
These fantastic Babble Balls are interactive toys that talk when touched. Packed with 20 different wisecracks and doggy-themed sounds. The improved technology is so sensitive it can be triggered by a dog breathing on it, or just by the vibration walking past it. When play is finished, the Babble Ball turns off automatically and waits to be touched again. Your dog will think it’s actually alive! 

Durable high impact ABS construction, triple the sounds, improved sound quality and now with replaceable batteries - great fun for you and your pooch! 6cm in diameter.

name: Small talking babble ball® interactive dog toy

The improved technology is so sensitive it can be triggered by a dog breathing on it, or just by the vibration walking past it. When play is finished, the Babble Ball turns off automatically and waits to be touched again. Your dog will think it’s actually alive!

We’ve yet to meet a dog that didn’t love this one! It’s waterproof! It floats! It flashes! – what more could a pooch want?

Flat, easy to grab, hold, and carry by almost any sized dog, these realistic animals will inspire your dog’s natural prey drive.

Features:
No stuffing, no mess!
2 squeakers (head and tail)
Realistic features
Machine washable
Durable
